{"tid":832150,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我真係好自卑","createTime":"2018-09-22T14:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T11:30:22.000Z","uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b1418c84d8289d0f255c587933a4e7b2913a035f","tid":832150,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T14:40:47.000Z","msg":"幾個月前因為跣親，成個膝蓋撞落地下<br />\n到依家都仲青黑，我睇見已經覺得冇得救，玩完<br />\n成個夏天都係著長褲渡過，見到人地可以著短褲真係羨慕又妒忌<br />\n覺得人地就好，對腳一d疤痕都冇，又白又滑<br />\n我以前都係，但依家就多咗疤痕，極自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82fd8752a6b41794bd3b136b40a748fc0baa20f","tid":832150,"uid":15184,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T15:26:46.000Z","msg":"有冇用去疤膏？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f6206be09da940732592fa77caef36ef373c4a","tid":832150,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a82fd8752a6b41794bd3b136b40a748fc0baa20f","tid":832150,"uid":15184,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T15:26:46.000Z","msg":"有冇用去疤膏？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T15:36:46.000Z","msg":"冇，但已經事隔幾個月，依家先嚟用會唔會太遲？"},{"pid":"f5035afbf3278cf1226b604cb5bec92979690224","tid":832150,"uid":50162,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T15:38:28.000Z","msg":"都唔知點解咁多負皮，嚟啦，踩我啦，依家呢個世界嘅人就係咁鐘意落井下石！"},{"pid":"55da46b03bb3a16451aa05583a9ab0b399a9882c","tid":832150,"uid":34927,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"f5035afbf3278cf1226b604cb5bec92979690224","tid":832150,"uid":50162,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T15:38:28.000Z","msg":"都唔知點解咁多負皮，嚟啦，踩我啦，依家呢個世界嘅人就係咁鐘意落井下石！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T15:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.laijiemi.com/uploads/allimg/161104/11392SG0-0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.laijiemi.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F161104%2F