3b5f3b13547f3283db32848379fb88502af7","tid":832150,"uid":82280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T17:04:41.000Z","msg":"廿幾仲好後生姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾啲時間佢"},{"pid":"c13fb605f347d76cc34754557244bdd4762e7e5c","tid":832150,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T17:13:55.000Z","msg":"經常做運動周身傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你個傷口好明顯好大?"},{"pid":"600ab137ee9488aa3f79be12426dd86e2151b43e","tid":832150,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c13fb605f347d76cc34754557244bdd4762e7e5c","tid":832150,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T17:13:55.000Z","msg":"經常做運動周身傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你個傷口好明顯好大?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T17:52:33.000Z","msg":"咁你周身傷痕會點處理？我就真係好少可，今次跣一跣好大件事，老實講膝蓋入面仍有痛，而個疤痕就正正係膝蓋正中位置，企係身伸直腳個膝蓋位會好明顯，我極自卑，以後冇得靚靚短裙，玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de71b40c07ecaa7dcf279cc52d84e27c71c1794","tid":832150,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"be8a3b5f3b13547f3283db32848379fb88502af7","tid":832150,"uid":82280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T17:04:41.000Z","msg":"廿幾仲好後生姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾啲時間佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T17:59:59.000Z","msg":"真係仲有得救？我唔知可以用咩方法，更何況已經事隔幾個月，我相信黑色素已完全沉澱，我以前冇得再著靚靚短裙，睇到人地一雙雙白滑美腿我真係極自卑，我以前都係，但我以後都唔會再係，點解又唔見呢d人跣下睇吓佢地有冇得咁得戚著短褲短裙通街演嘢！個天今次畀咗一個好大嘅懲罰我！"},{"pid":"f174f5bb299aafacc76ec81b0d3e75727e8acab6","tid":832150,"uid":29226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T18:17:25.000Z","msg":"毛囊角化 成個小腿都係紅點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 照著短褲"},{"pid":"75166f661217b78da60c828bb418a46510bd0e78","tid":832150,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T18:20:05.000Z","msg":"斬咗隻腳 裝上義肢 會有種楚楚可憐嘅缺陷美"},{"pid":"351e4acbd06dcfd82c8e854d703cafa13776e088","tid":832150,"uid":5959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T18:25:33.000Z","msg":"你維持心情差對復原影響仲大<br />\n做吓運動血液循環好啲，遲早散<br />\n無得露腳咪露住心口先囉"},{"pid":"2abd944a8690914eb20ce3cb84cd859127abdd16","tid":832150,"uid":59069,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T12:03:05.000Z","msg":"咩都唔做又喺到話唔掂唔掂<br />\n都唔知你做乜鳩<br />\n除疤膏又冇試過 又話自己廿幾歲會一路咁<br />\n唔通你日日望住個膝頭會自己靚返咩<br />\n<br />\n想整返靚著短褲短裙咪整靚返佢囉 <br />\n咪撚再怨啦 落樓下買除疤膏試左先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c38e506cc708a4cb9e79f31b0abc2fdee91dab","tid":832150,"uid":115910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T12:04:32.000Z","msg":"你呢啲撚樣老左肯定係俾蚊針一野都對住仔女哭喪咁既麻閪煩老野"},{"pid":"cae7807815def5e8e71b13801b5fbd9a04c70bbb","tid":832150,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T12:05:38.000Z","msg":"好少事姐"},{"pid":"34186945cc768e96aa734eea295f2d76050a6364","tid":832150,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T13:40:00.000Z","msg":"今朝去咗睇X光，個醫生話冇事，問個膝蓋有疤痕有黑青，佢話做咩都唔會有用<br />\n哈哈哈，我正式玩完啦，之後都冇心機去返工，各位負皮者開心啦，哈哈哈哈！"},{"pid":"b2fb6d48bd367b551541572f92e33d04f3d84fd0","tid":832150,"uid":211716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34186945cc768e96aa734eea295f2d76050a6364","tid":832150,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T13:40:00.000Z","msg":"今朝去咗睇X光，個醫生話冇事，問個膝蓋有疤痕有黑青，佢話做咩都唔會有用<br />\n哈哈哈，我正式玩完啦，之後都冇心機去返工，各位負皮者開心啦，哈哈哈哈！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T13:43:26.000Z","msg":"醫生都話無事你悲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會因為呢兩個傷口嫁唔出？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係既呢啲男人要唔要都擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"530a39e828fc26927f3adf9a2834ad886013c00c","tid":832150,"uid":